dmca.title: Blogger's images don't entertain O&C Entertainment
dmca.body:
To whom it may concern, 

I have discovered that a breach of our copyright is taking place in the following blog at www.blogger.com:

http://cfnmpics.blogspot.com/
 
All of these images are from a site I own and are clearly marked with our URL.  The address is www.cfnm.net.
 
My address is: 
0 & C Entertainment 
[private]
Lloyds Court 
0 & C Entertainment
London 
EI 8AT 
UK 

I have a good faith belief that use of the copyrighted materials described above on the allegedly infringing webpages is not authorized by the copyright owner, its agent, or the law.
